Introducing our futuristic 6 nozzle dispenser across Pakistan






Announcement of Final Cash Dividend
The Board of Directors of the Company in their meeting held on 31st March 2017 has approved the annual accounts for the period ended 31st December 2016 and has declared a Final Cash Dividend of Rs. 3.50 per share i.e. 35%. This is in addition to the interim cash dividend of Rs. 3.50 per share i.e. 35%, already paid. The total dividend for the year 2016 is 70% Cash Dividend.





